<template>
    <v-dialog :value="dialog" max-width="500px">
      <!-- ... rest of your dialog component -->
    </v-dialog>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    props: {
      appointment: {
        type: Object,
        required: true,
      },
      dialog: {
        type: Boolean,
        required: true,
      },
    },
    methods: {
      closeDialog() {
        this.$emit('close-dialog'); // Emit an event to request closing the dialog
      },
    },
  };
  </script>
